{
  "id": "6a2bc7e65de9cd7978eae394",
  "title": "笑いながら考える人",
  "created": 1781254121,
  "updated": 1781309686,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2bc7e65de9cd7978eae394",
      "text": "笑いながら考える人",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781254121,
      "updated": 1781254121
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2bc81200000000008d7cbc",
      "text": " [思想家]にしても[哲学者]にしても、[考える人]はなぜ大体暗いのか[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781254201,
      "updated": 1781254308
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2bc82700000000008d7cbd",
      "text": "  笑いながら考える人がいてもいいと思う",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781254222,
      "updated": 1781254263
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2bc7c100000000008d7cb9",
      "text": "   [https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.F85E/0758-8BD0.webp?20260612174803]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781254121,
      "updated": 1781254265
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2c7a230000000000a229a8",
      "text": "    私は大体こんな感じで考え事をしている",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781299747,
      "updated": 1781302109
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2c9fac0000000000046076",
      "text": "   笑うたびに顎に当てている手が痛くなりそう[hayai.icon]",
      "userId": "66bd5a5862236d001dbc64c4",
      "created": 1781309357,
      "updated": 1781309387
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2c9fdd0000000000046077",
      "text": "    実際にやってみたら、手ではなく顎への負担が半端じゃなかった",
      "userId": "66bd5a5862236d001dbc64c4",
      "created": 1781309406,
      "updated": 1781309503
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2ca00b0000000000046078",
      "text": "    これのせいでみんな笑うのやめとこう、となってしまうのかも",
      "userId": "66bd5a5862236d001dbc64c4",
      "created": 1781309452,
      "updated": 1781309636
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2ca04e0000000000046079",
      "text": "    顎が屈強な選ばれし者が生き残る世界",
      "userId": "66bd5a5862236d001dbc64c4",
      "created": 1781309519,
      "updated": 1781309596
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2ca0e9000000000004607a",
      "text": "    顎下は自由であるべき",
      "userId": "66bd5a5862236d001dbc64c4",
      "created": 1781309674,
      "updated": 1781309686
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2c832a000000000067cebe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781302098,
      "updated": 1781302098
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2bc7c200000000008d7cba",
      "text": "\t考えながらニヤける、は結構やる[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1781254121,
      "updated": 1781299751
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2c7a210000000000a229a7",
      "text": "　なぜか「[戦いながら考える人]」に空目した[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781299746,
      "updated": 1781301525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2c80f30000000000cfb376",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781301491,
      "updated": 1781301491
    }
  ]
}